lead_paragraph: John Wall scored 24 points with 13 assists, Otto Porter had 20 points and 11 rebounds, and the Washington Wizards extended their dominance over the Orlando Magic with a 103-91 victory Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Wall, Porter Lead Wizards to 103-91 Win Over Magic
